Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.13,0:00:39.56,OPCH3,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(100,100)}你「我」的東西 皆為我有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:42.89,OPCH3,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(100,100)}沒錯 為了有所實現
